r country settings</a></li><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a data-article="20169405" href="/articles/20169405">Changing your time zone settings</a></li></ul></li><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a class="has-articles" data-category="313" href="#"><i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i><span>Account insights</span></a><ul class="leftnav-group" role="menu"><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a data-article="20170160" href="/articles/20170160">Downloading your Twitter archive</a></li><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a data-article="20172496" href="/articles/20172496">Account home</a></li><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a data-article="20169409" href="/articles/20169409">About media timelines in profiles</a></li><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a data-article="20171990" href="/articles/20171990">Tweet activity dashboard</a></li><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a data-article="20172679" href="/articles/20172679">Accessing your Twitter data</a></li></ul></li><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a class="has-articles" data-category="314" href="#"><i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i><span>Verified accounts</span></a><ul class="leftnav-group" role="menu"><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a data-article="119135" href="/articles/119135">FAQs about verified accounts</a></li></ul></li><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a class="has-articles" data-category="315" href="#"><i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i><span>Reactivate or deactivate an account</span></a><ul class="leftnav-group" role="menu"><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a data-article="15359" href="/articles/15359">Reactivating your account</a></li><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a data-article="15358" href="/articles/15358">Deactivating your account</a></li></ul></li><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a class="leftnav-back" href="#"><i class="fa fa-chevron-left"></i> Back</a></li></ul></li>
